pwncat
Fancy reverse and bind shell handler

Maintaining Access
Description
pwncat is a post-exploitation platform for Linux and Windows targets. It features automated enumeration and persistence modules.

Installation / Check
Check if installed:

which pwncat
Install command:

pip install pwncat-cs
Basic Syntax
pwncat-cs [options]
Common Commands
Command	What it does	When to use	Risk
pwncat-cs -lp 4444

Start listener	Catch reverse shell	
run enumerate

Auto enumeration	Gather system info	
run persist.cron

Cron persistence	Maintain access	
upload local remote

Upload file	Transfer files	
privesc.auto

Auto privesc	Escalate privileges	
